data.title: GoldenSource Corporation: Revenue, Competitors, Alternatives
data.meta_description: GoldenSource Corporation top competitors are SoluLab, Luminati Networks and Guidepoint and they have annual revenue of $118.9M  and 656  employees.
data.text:
FTI is the premier solution provider of financial enterprise software for global banking and securities firms by providing a single operating platform and a complete suite of enterprise applications. Spanning more than 18 years, FTI has built up a clientele consisting of the most prestigious and demanding customers. Today, FTI is the leading provider of financial enterprise software with a global reach across three continents
